<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首尾有1法，方法二：被乘数首位带1与乘数末位带1的两位数的乘法时，可先根据乘法交换律，交换其被乘数与乘数的位置后，再利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">10ad+[10×(10a+1)+d]</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a分别表示乘数个位上的数字，d表示被乘数十位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">15×71=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 15×71</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=71×15</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=10×7×5+(10×71+5)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=350+(710+5)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=350+715</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1065</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>